buyer_tax_number.description: Buyer's tax number - EU VAT number for example. buyer_tax_number_valid.description: If the buyer tax number has been provided and was validated successfully. Always true for domestic transactions (billing country same as merchant's country), tax number doesn't get validated in that case.

tax_deducted.description: If the transaction is in a country supported by Taxamo, but the tax is not calculated due to merchant settings or EU B2B transaction for example.
